overview.en: The GSTEA open financial system platform aims to develop a complete cross-chain decentralized financial ecosystem, creating a decentralized wallet, lending, financing, trading, prediction and other DeFi technology facilities integrated, cross-chain technology and financial services ecology.
overview.zh: GSTEA开放式金融系统平台，旨在开发一个完备跨链的去中心化金融生态系统，打造去中心化钱包、借贷、融资、交易、预言等DeFi技术设施为一体、跨链的科技金融服务生态。
